{"tid":2299141,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[有線] 保皇黨如何「製造」民意？","createTime":"2020-11-24T14:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T11:57:56.000Z","uid":301666,"like":74,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"ede64547978db8321a87b7153305b3e09f0aa523","tid":2299141,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:06:11.000Z","msg":"呢幾個月，大家係咪喺黨媒見到唔同嘅民調，全部都話<span class=\"red\"><strong>支持港共／中共施政</strong></span>呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/123481344_216882083205492_8832289376286468285_n.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=SygFI_eNKtwAX_AkoRA&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;oh=129dc46fcf3e8625a16d8f678f0e3bf5&amp;oe=5FE2CCF7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F123481344_216882083205492_8832289376286468285_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DSygFI_eNKtwAX_AkoRA%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26oh%3D129dc46fcf3e8625a16d8f678f0e3bf5%26oe%3D5FE2CCF7&h=9ceaabad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有線新聞刺針就做咗個調查，睇下呢啲民調係點嚟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/news.lancet/videos/152401313278451\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnews.lancet%2Fvideos%2F152401313278451&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKHqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=7e82538b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/news.lancet/videos/152401313278451</a><br />\n<br />\n原來主要係兩間機構，個名叫<span class=\"red\"><strong>青研香港</strong></span>，同埋<strong><span class=\"red\">公民社會研究所</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n等我哋睇下佢哋點做調查啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n公民社會研究所：<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/11/24/r8ly7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F11%2F24%2Fr8ly7A.jpg&h=c7052b35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n利用<strong><span class=\"red\">支那平台</span></strong>做取樣方法，真係夠晒代表性！<br />\n<br />\n再睇下發言人點樣解釋：<br />\n<br />\n「我覺得真實，個真實係在於我哋攞嘅數據係真實，個真實嘅現況就係<span class=\"red\"><strong>有人缺席咗無參賽姐</strong></span>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/11/24/miQapD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F11%2F24%2FmiQapD.jpg&h=d638e914&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n青研香港：<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/11/24/Pf6Xdh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F11%2F24%2FPf6Xdh.jpg&h=5605b519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n清一色用建制派平台搜集資料真係多謝晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發言人：「 反映唔到香港整體市民嘅意見，唔代表佢係一份無參考價值嘅民調囉」<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/11/24/1zJWtr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F11%2F24%2F1zJWtr.jpg&h=c8fae294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家咁就見到<span class=\"red\">保皇黨點樣偽造民意，企圖篡改歷史</span>啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再Post多次條Link，入面有片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/news.lancet/videos/152401313278451\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnews.lancet%2Fvideos%2F152401313278451&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKHqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=7e82538b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/news.lancet/videos/152401313278451</a>"},{"pid":"bb1d6264a30920c9755dd0948b29de7efd06a8a5","tid":2299141,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:07:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f80bf043ef057405df929326115c109048a5c0","tid":2299141,"uid":10998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0b65b3615e74ce4abcf8663d59513d776aeb01","tid":2299141,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:08:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c5f20405d43f55b2d8e61f29c33b8af0dd2d0ec4","tid":2299141,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:09:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d790692d6b4ca08404a47be2c79f2f6271191b23","tid":2299141,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:09:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4319158cbc045321937c4b1750a79af14c763ad7","tid":2299141,"uid":299134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a6f7198f1d0f167568c06416cfde6ebf92b19e","tid":2299141,"uid":301666,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:10:40.000Z","msg":"「民調」機構：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://x7n5x3t5.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/%E9%A3%9F%E9%9B%9E%E7%8F%8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fx7n5x3t5.stackpathcdn.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2F%25E9%25A3%259F%25E9%259B%259E%25E7%258F%258D.jpg&h=fd013985&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"511b962431bb440e8d9a143b43bbc88cff6d5075","tid":2299141,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:14:36.000Z","msg":"新聞刺針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2c6d36d2e11aa76849b3a15867ba7db6cdd8ef","tid":2299141,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:15:14.000Z","msg":"支那成撚日自己呃鼠己，舊年區選都係咁樣比香港人離棄變少數派"},{"pid":"73f630c4e4d1e1f91f81be34eec49f63bc54fbd9","tid":2299141,"uid":301666,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:17:15.000Z","msg":"比大家欣賞下傑出例子：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>十二港人：</strong></span>「公民社會研究所」喺本月18至20日期間以網上問卷訪問咗2262人，結果聲稱有<span class=\"red\">近九成受訪者</span>認為內地司法機關處理內地觸犯法律港人案件嘅安排「非常恰當」。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>教育局釘牌：</strong></span> 逾<span class=\"red\">9成半人</span>認同相關教材有散播「獨暴」元素，<span class=\"red\">八成受訪者</span>認為教育局對案件的處理恰當<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">司法改革：</span></strong> 絕大部分受訪者均認為「有需要」或「非常有需要」進行司法機構改革，當中<span class=\"red\">約八成</span>認為應設立獨立的「監察司法委員會」及「量刑委員會」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">全民檢測</span></strong>：公民社會研究所於本周二、三，以網上問卷方式訪問10419人，發現<span class=\"red\">89.23%受訪者</span>表示一定會，或應該會參與全民檢測。"},{"pid":"f4b4bb1b69c5729ef35b607deff979e6f6d724ad","tid":2299141,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612bc85e34a070bb1fea8dd3e55a05d0cd799e97","tid":2299141,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:17:42.000Z","msg":"有線泄露國家機密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efddcff79e4de95cffcee7f506a62f7cc0a2e020","tid":2299141,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:24:22.000Z","msg":"笑死"},{"pid":"768359f4f022ae87c2a61e70f972ca80a67fd5dd","tid":2299141,"uid":313162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3e1cba2b87538622979818c8b97df21eca5a42","tid":2299141,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:27:34.000Z","msg":"陳志豪自己最清楚自己有冇講大話"},{"pid":"24f1388e9f7e9e21ebbee40d0e0f4a1a8a4a0b26","tid":2299141,"uid":301666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c3e1cba2b87538622979818c8b97df21eca5a42","tid":2299141,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:27:34.000Z","msg":"陳志豪自己最清楚自己有冇講大話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:28:48.000Z","msg":"曾參與2019年區議會選舉西貢區議會德明選區，但以4217票對5240票<span class=\"red\"><strong>不敵民主派</strong></span>候選人鄭仲文。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.